                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Up to three reminder emails, if necessary</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">A brief (10–15-minute) survey focused on universities within your academic discipline</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Full confidentiality: responses are anonymous and reported only in aggregated form</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">No promotional messages or third-party use of your information</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">The option to decline participation at any stage, should you change your mind</li>
